title: Windows 8 Add-On Setup Programs - Start Button Back,Gadgets etc
description:
Windows 8 Add-On Setup Programs - Start Button Back,Gadgets etc


I put a collection of programs I always install on a new PC
with windows 8 

-Classic Shell (adds start menu .taskbar back!)
-Access control TWEAKERUI (can disable or put to quiet to rid annoying popups)
handy when install new software. wizard backs it easy to turn on and off
but reboot is needed
-Desktop Gadgets.. get your favourire CPU meter and clock down the right side
- Process Lasso.. like task manager but can monitor and control out of control
programs. free version only but min nags appear.. cheap to upgrade too
if like it. 64bit only version but 32bit is about and free to download
on their website
-Teracopy
-Live Mail Installer
-and more tweaks like adding gpedit for home versions

just unzip.unrar the enclose file to a folder 
and install each as normal

HELP seed I have slow ISP and limited DATA cheers

ENJOY!
